g.text: Edge Case Decision Map: Scanner Logic (scanner.py)

ol.li: O(n) Time: Every character visited exactly once via advance().
Non-decreasing Columns: Token column always increases within a line.
Sentinel Integrity: Every stream MUST end with TokenType.EOF.

text.tspan: Panic-mode recovery: advance 1 char and resume.
Digit scan terminates at non-digit boundary.
